data.description: LUXURY WATERFRONT ESTATE in the Heart of Trent Woods! European Style Custom Home built in 2014 with MAJESTIC COLUMNS AND GATED ENTRY leading up to 4-Car Courtyard Garage on a PRIVATE ROAD. The RIVERFRONT VIEWS WILL TAKE YOUR BREATH AWAY! Elegant Grand Foyer and Salon with stately columns, marble flooring Fireplace and sweeping two-story river views.  Magnificent Entertainment Area off of the Reception Hall with built-in bench seating, granite, custom cabinetry, sink, refrigerator and icemaker.  Gourmet Kitchen with 3 ovens, a 6-burner gas range, mother of pearl backsplash, marble countertops, bar seating, and travertine flooring. Adjacent Dining and Den are appointed with 10-foot columns, cathedral ceiling and STUNNING WATER VIEWS!  Formal Dining Room with custom mouldings. Two Powder Rooms on the main floor, 12-inch crown and wainscoting.  Utility/Laundry off of the kitchen has a built-in marble desk and cabinetry. The Study has French glass doors and built-in cabinetry. Master Suite features cathedral ceilings, gorgeous hardwoods, and stunning water views!  The adjoining Master Bath is spa worthy with marble flooring, chandeliers, columns, whirlpool, and his/her water closets. Additional laundry with laundry chute off of Hallway.  The custom curved wrought iron staircase leads to the second floor with catwalk and viewing arch over the Salon. There are  4 additional Bedrooms with gorgeous water views, walk-in closets, and adjoining baths with marble flooring. Exercise room off of the main hallway. Storage Galore, and SPECTACULAR VIEWS FROM EVERY ROOM!  The outside patios are accessible from Den and Master Suite and overlook the Trent River with abundant wildlife and tranquil breezes. Ospreys and cranes grace the skies throughout the day.  Enjoy the  MAGNIFICENT SUNSETS while relaxing or entertaining. Two 10,000 lb BOAT LIFTS on the Dock for your enjoyment.  DON'T MISS THIS BEAUTY!
